<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ميلاد يسوع</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ميلاد يسوع عشاني كان لأنه حبني

[V2]
 ساب السما وجاني يغفر لي خطيتي

[V3]
 مش في قصر ولا فيلا ولا برج عالي رهيب

[V4]
 ملك الملوك في مزود مولود في تواضع عجيب

[V5]
 والكل ليه جه يسجد: مجوس وكمان رعاة

[V6]
 ملايكة بتقول: ليه المجد جالنا فقير برغم غناه

[V7]
 قلبي وحبي ليك هدايا وحياتي يا يسوع

[V8]
 ده حبك لي كفايا أنت أعظم حب يا يسوع You know dasher, and dancer and Prancer, and

[V9]
 Vixen, comet, and cupid, and Donder and Blitzen

[V10]
 But do you recall

[V11]
 The most famous reindeer of all Rubdolh, the red-

[V12]
 Nosed reindeer had a very shiny nose

[V13]
 And if you ever saw him, you would even say it glows.

[V14]
 All of the other reindeer used to laugh and call him

[V15]
 Names. They never let poor Rudolph

[V16]
 Join in any reindeer games
 Une fee qui lentendit pleurer dans le noir

[V17]
 Pour le consoler, lui dit: viens au paradis, ce soir.

[V18]
 Comme un ange, nez Rouge Tu conduiras dans le ciel

[V19]
 Avec ton ptit nez rouge Le chariot du pere-noel

[V20]
 Quand la neige recouvre la verte Finlande

[V21]
 Et que les rennes traversent la lande

[V22]
 Le vent dans la unit Au troupeau, parle encore de lui Rudolph, the red-nosed reindeer

[V23]
 Had a very shiny nose And if you ever saw him

[V24]
 You would even say it glows. All of the other reindeer

[V25]
 Used to laugh and call him names.

[V26]
 They never let poor Rudolph

[V27]
 Join in any reindeer games Vous fillettes et garcons, pour la grand nuit

[V28]
 Si vous savez vos lecons des que sonnera minuit

[V29]
 Ce petit point qui bouge, Ainsi qu une etoile au loin

[V30]
 Cest le nez de Nez Rouge Annoncant le pere-noel (3)</lyrics>
